  "instructions": [
    "Combine flour, butter, and salt in a bowl to create the pastry dough.",
    "Add the egg and knead for 5 minutes until smooth.",
    "Place the dough in the refrigerator for 10 minutes.",
    "Roll out the dough to a thickness of 5mm.",
    "Place the trout fillet in the center of the dough and brush with lemon juice.",
    "Fold the dough over the trout and press edges to seal.",
    "Preheat a large skillet over medium heat and cook for 8 minutes on each side.",
    "Serve warm with a side of your choice."
